                  <summary> Thirukkural Uraiyudan refers to a Tamil text where the classic philosophical work "Thirukkural" is presented with detailed commentary and explanation, essentially providing a deeper understanding of the verses by elucidating their meaning and context, often exploring their ethical and moral implications in a modern light; "Uraiyudan" literally translates to "with explanation" in Tamil, signifying the commentary aspect of the text.   </summary>
                  
